# hindsight_sync_retain --bank_id documentation --content "# Readme\n\n# Graphify Neo4j Database\n\nNeo4j graph database export of the Graphify knowledge graph.\n\n## Quick Start\n\n```bash\n# Automated setup (recommended)\n./setup.sh\n\n# Manual setup\ndocker-compose up -d\n```\n\n## Access Neo4j\n\n- **Browser**: http://localhost:7474\n- **Username**: `neo4j`\n- **Password**: `graphify123`\n\n## Import Data\n\n1. Open Neo4j Browser: http://localhost:7474\n2. Login with credentials above\n3. Copy queries from `import.cypher`\n4. Paste into Neo4j Browser and execute\n\n## Files\n\n- `nodes.csv` - 30,724 nodes\n- `relationships.csv` - 58,982 relationships\n- `import.cypher` - Import script\n- `queries.cypher` - 25+ example queries\n- `docker-compose.yml` - Neo4j setup\n- `setup.sh` - Automated setup\n\n## Example Queries\n\nSee `queries.cypher` for full list.\n\n### Basic Exploration\n```cypher\n// Sample nodes\nMATCH (n) RETURN n LIMIT 25;\n\n// Community sizes\nMATCH (n) \nRETURN n.community, count(*) as size \nORDER BY size DESC \nLIMIT 10;\n```\n\n### Find Hubs\n```cypher\nMATCH (n)\nWITH n, size((n)--()) as degree\nWHERE degree > 10\nRETURN n.label, degree\nORDER BY degree DESC;\n```\n\n### Path Finding\n```cypher\nMATCH (start {label: 'Memory'}), (end {label: 'documents'})\nMATCH path = shortestPath((start)-[*..5]-(end))\nRETURN path;\n```\n\n## Troubleshooting\n\n**Can't connect?**\n- Wait 30 seconds after `docker-compose up`\n- Check: `docker ps` shows neo4j running\n- View logs: `docker-compose logs -f neo4j`\n\n**Import fails?**\n- Ensure APOC plugin is loaded\n- Run queries one at a time\n- Check CSV files are in import/ directory\n\n## Stop Neo4j\n\n```bash\ndocker-compose down\n```\n\n## Full Documentation\n\nSee `../GRAPHIFY_VISUALIZATIONS_GUIDE.md` for complete documentation.\n" --context documentation --tags "source:docs,type:documentation"

