# hindsight_sync_retain --bank_id documentation --content "# Settings Registry\n\n# Settings Registry\n\nWP-02 | feat/settings-registry\n\n---\n\n## Purpose\n\nCentralize all runtime configuration for the CollabMind platform.\nReplaces scattered `.env` variables with a governed, versioned, auditable registry.\nSecrets are stored as references only — never as raw values.\n\n---\n\n## Tables\n\n| Table | Purpose |\n|-------|---------|\n| `platform_settings` | Tenant/workspace-scoped key/value runtime config |\n| `platform_setting_versions` | Immutable mutation history per setting |\n| `platform_secrets` | Secret metadata + external `secret_ref` only |\n| `service_config_cache` | Per-service resolved config status tracker |\n\n---\n\n## Secret Ref Rule\n\n**Never store raw secret values in the database, docs, logs, or API responses.**\n\nAll secrets use a `secret_ref` URI pointing to the actual value in an external system:\n\n| Scheme | Example |\n|--------|---------|\n| `env://` | `env://OPENAI_API_KEY` |\n| `vault://` | `vault://secret/collabmind/openai` |\n| `authentik://` | `authentik://client-secret/collabmind-api` |\n| `cloudflare-secret://` | `cloudflare-secret://openai-key` |\n\nDB-level `CHECK` constraints enforce this. If `encrypted=true`, `value_json` must be `NULL` and `secret_ref` must be set.\n\n---\n\n## Allowed Setting Types\n\n| Type | Used For |\n|------|----------|\n| `string` | Text values, URLs, identifiers |\n| `number` | Counts, limits, timeouts |\n| `boolean` | Feature flags |\n| `json` | Structured config objects |\n| `secret` | Always use `encrypted=true` + `secret_ref` |\n\n---\n\n## Service Key Naming Convention\n\n`service_key` must match the service name in `SERVICE_REGISTRY.md`.\n\nExamples:\n- `model-gateway`\n- `documents`\n- `memory-controller`\n- `evaluation`\n- `qdrant`\n- `authentik`\n- `mcp-gateway`\n\n---\n\n## Example Settings\n\n```json\n{\n  \"service_key\": \"model-gateway\",\n  \"setting_key\": \"default_model\",\n  \"setting_type\": \"string\",\n  \"value_json\": \"grok-3\",\n  \"encrypted\": false,\n  \"scope\": \"global\",\n  \"environment\": \"production\"\n}\n```\n\n```json\n{\n  \"service_key\": \"model-gateway\"" --context documentation --tags "source:docs,type:documentation"

