# hindsight_sync_retain --bank_id documentation --content "# Auth Route Policy\n\n# Auth Route Policy\n\nWP-03 | feat/auth-mcp-stabilization\nLast updated: 2026-06-06\n\n---\n\n## Rule: Two Auth Surfaces\n\n| Surface | Caller | Required Auth | On Failure |\n|---------|--------|---------------|------------|\n| **Browser / Operator** | Human via collabmind-console | Authentik OIDC (RS256 JWT) | Redirect to Authentik login |\n| **Machine / MCP / Agent** | API client, MCP tool, internal service | `X-Api-Key` header OR `Authorization: Bearer <jwt>` | JSON `401` — no redirect |\n\n---\n\n## Route Classification\n\n| Path | Auth Required | Allowed Methods | Notes |\n|------|--------------|-----------------|-------|\n| `GET /health` | None — public | Any | No auth check |\n| `GET /auth/me` | Required — any method | JWT, API key | Returns `req.context` if valid; 401 otherwise |\n| `POST /auth/*` | None (callback/verify routes) | Any | NextAuth callbacks; no auth gate |\n| `GET /platform/status` | Required | JWT, API key | — |\n| `/api/*` | Required | JWT, API key | JSON 401/403 only — **never HTML redirect** |\n| `/mcp/*` | Required | JWT, API key | JSON 401/403 only — **never HTML redirect** |\n\n---\n\n## Accepted Auth Methods\n\n### 1. Authentik RS256 JWT (Bearer)\n\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer <jwt>\n```\n\n- Verified against Authentik JWKS endpoint (`AUTHENTIK_JWKS_URL`)\n- Algorithm: RS256 only\n- Issuer validated: `AUTHENTIK_ISSUER_URL`\n- Claims mapped to context:\n  - `sub` → `tenant_id`, `actor_id`, `user_id`\n  - `aud` → `source_app_id`\n  - `groups` → `roles`\n  - `scope` → `scopes`\n  - `auth_method` = `'jwt'`\n\n### 2. Service Token (Bearer)\n\nSame path as JWT Bearer. A service account JWT issued by Authentik for a machine client.\nNo special handling required — verified by the same RS256/JWKS path.\n\n### 3. X-Api-Key\n\n```\nX-Api-Key: <key>\n```\n\n- Looked up against `api_keys` table (migration 15, WP-15)\n- `key_hash` = raw key value (hash in DB if WP-15 implements hashing)\n- Expiry checked: `expires_at IS NULL OR expires_at > NOW()`\n- Claims from DB row: `tenant_id`, `actor_id`, `source_app_id" --context documentation --tags "source:docs,type:documentation"

