# hindsight_sync_retain --bank_id documentation --content "# Infra Reuse Map\n\n# Infrastructure Reuse Map — WP-00A\n\nRead-only source: `/Users/oliververmeulen/XAI/OpenMemory`\nTarget: `/Users/oliververmeulen/XAI/collabmind-stack`\nDate: 2026-06-06\n\n> Patterns only. Do not copy secrets or .env values.\n> Do not execute `update_cf_tunnel.py` or any tunnel scripts.\n> Do not modify old Traefik, Caddy, or tunnel configuration.\n\n---\n\n## Routing Layer\n\n### Traefik (`traefik/traefik.yml` + `traefik/dynamic.yml`)\n\n**Pattern extracted:**\n\n```yaml\n# traefik.yml — entry points pattern\nentryPoints:\n  web:    \":8006\"   # HTTP\n  traefik: \":8007\"  # Dashboard\n\nproviders:\n  file:\n    filename: /etc/traefik/dynamic.yml\n    watch: true     # hot-reload on change\n\napi:\n  dashboard: true\n  insecure: true    # dashboard accessible without auth (internal only)\n```\n\n**Dynamic routing** (`dynamic.yml` — 10KB, extensively configured):\n- Router → middleware chains\n- Forward-auth middleware (calls JWT validator sidecar at port 9000)\n- TLS passthrough patterns\n- Service definitions with load balancer URLs\n\n**Assessment for new stack**: The new stack uses **Caddy** as the reverse proxy (already in `collabmind-stack/Caddyfile`). Traefik patterns are reference only. Forward-auth pattern is replaced by `requireAuth()` middleware in Central API.\n\n### Caddy (`caddy/Caddyfile`)\n\n**Current old-stack config:**\n```\n{\n    auto_https off\n    admin off\n}\n:80 {\n    reverse_proxy openmemory-py:8082 {\n        header_up X-API-Key {\$OM_API_KEY}   # injects API key header\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Useful pattern**: `header_up` to inject API key into upstream requests. The new stack's `collabmind-stack/Caddyfile` (2147 bytes) is already more complete.\n\n---\n\n## Monitoring (`monitoring/`)\n\n### Prometheus (`monitoring/prometheus.yml`)\n\n**Pattern extracted:**\n\n```yaml\n# scrape config pattern (no secrets)\nscrape_configs:\n  - job_name: '<service>'\n    static_configs:\n      - targets: ['<host>:<port>']\n    scrape_interval: 15s\n```\n\nServices scraped: openmemory-py, postgres-exporter, redis/valkey, caddy, traefik\n\n" --context documentation --tags "source:docs,type:documentation"

