# hindsight_sync_retain --bank_id documentation --content "# Readme\n\n# CollabMind Stack Scripts\n\nHelper scripts for managing the control plane deployment.\n\n## Available Scripts\n\n| Script | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| `start.sh` | Start the full control plane stack |\n| `stop.sh` | Stop the control plane stack |\n| `status.sh` | Check health of all services |\n| `migrate.sh` | Run database migrations in order |\n\n## Usage\n\n```bash\n# Start everything\n./scripts/start.sh\n\n# Check status\n./scripts/status.sh\n\n# Run migrations\n./scripts/migrate.sh\n\n# Stop everything\n./scripts/stop.sh\n```\n\n## Prerequisites\n- Docker and Docker Compose installed\n- `.env` file configured from `.env.example`\n- Services built (first run will build images)\n" --context documentation --tags "source:docs,type:documentation"

