# hindsight_sync_retain --bank_id documentation --content "# Readme\n\n# CollabMind Dev Stack\n\nLocal integrated stack for the governed CollabMind control plane.\n\nThe implemented `central-api` in this stack is the TypeScript service under `stacks/collabmind/api`. It is the public control-plane surface for local dev. Backend engines stay internal unless you explicitly enable optional profiles.\n\n## Quick Start\n\n```bash\ncd /Users/oliververmeulen/XAI-v2/stacks/collabmind/deploy/dev\ncp .env.example .env\n\n# Start the core local stack\ndocker compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml up --build -d\n\n# Apply the control-plane migration\ndocker compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml run --rm central-api-migrate\n\n# Run the integration smoke checks\n../scripts/dev-smoke.sh\n```\n\n## Default Services\n\n| Service | Host Port | Role |\n|---------|-----------|------|\n| `central-api` | `3050` | Governed public control plane |\n| `collabmind-console` | `3060` | Operator UI |\n| `qdrant` | `6333` on `127.0.0.1` only | Local vector engine for dev |\n| `postgres` | not exposed | Control-plane source of truth |\n| `valkey` | not exposed | Internal cache/queue |\n| `memory-controller` | not exposed | Internal memory orchestration |\n| `documents` | not exposed | Internal ingestion pipeline |\n| `model-gateway` | not exposed | Internal model routing |\n| `evaluation` | not exposed | Internal evaluation service |\n| `collabmind-mcp` | not exposed | Internal stdio MCP gateway |\n\nOptional profiles:\n- `dashboards`: adds `vector-admin` on `3080`\n- `engines`: adds internal `memlord` and `openmemory` containers\n\n## Architecture\n\n```text\nAgent / MCP client\n  -> collabmind-mcp (stdio)\n  -> central-api\n  -> governance / auth / audit / permissions\n  -> memory-controller / documents / model-gateway\n  -> Postgres / Qdrant / optional MemLord / optional OpenMemory\n```\n\n## Verification\n\nThe smoke script checks:\n- compose renders\n- migration applies and records `001_initial_schema.sql`\n- `/health`\n- `/api/health/engines`\n- audit persistence\n- connector route smoke for Google Drive stubs\n- MCP `platform_he" --context documentation --tags "source:docs,type:documentation"

