# hindsight_sync_retain --bank_id documentation --content "# Mcp Tools\n\n# MCP Tools Reference\n\n## Runtime Mode\n\nSet `COLLABMIND_MCP_MODE` to select routing mode:\n\n| Value | Default | Description |\n|-------|---------|-------------|\n| `central_api` | ✅ yes | All tools route through Central API at `:3050` |\n| `direct_dev` | no | Tools route directly to per-service ports — **local testing only** |\n\n**DIRECT_DEV_MODE bypasses the Central API edge and is for local testing only.**\nDirect dev mode is blocked when `NODE_ENV=production`.\n\n---\n\n## Central API (:3050) Status\n\n**`:3050` verified live** (2026-06-12, dev mode, `DATABASE_URL=postgresql://localhost:5432/collabmind_dev`)\n\nAuth: `X-Api-Key` header. All routes require a valid API key except `GET /health`.\n\n---\n\n## CENTRAL_API_MODE (`COLLABMIND_MCP_MODE=central_api`)\n\nAll routes go through `collabmind-api` at `:3050`.\n\n| Tool | Route | Backend | Status |\n|------|-------|---------|--------|\n| `platform_health` | `GET /health` | collabmind-api | ✅ verified via :3050 |\n| `memory_search` | `POST /api/memory/search` | memory-controller :3020 | ✅ verified via :3050 |\n| `memory_store` | `POST /api/memory` | memory-controller :3020 | ✅ verified via :3050 |\n| `correction_store` | `POST /api/memory/correction` | memory-controller :3020 | ✅ verified via :3050 |\n| `policy_check` | `POST /api/memory/governance/policy-check` | memory-controller :3020 | ✅ verified via :3050 |\n| `tenant_export` | `GET /api/memory/export` | memory-controller :3020 | ✅ verified via :3050 |\n| `document_search` | `POST /api/documents/search` | documents :3030 | ✅ route verified via :3050 — 400 from :3030 (no embedding profile seeded) |\n| `retrieval_run` | `POST /api/retrieval/run` | documents :3030 | ✅ route verified via :3050 — 400 from :3030 (no embedding profile seeded) |\n| `get_trace` | `GET /api/retrieval/runs/:id` | documents :3030 | ✅ route verified via :3050 |\n| `model_call` | `POST /api/model/call` | model-gateway :3031 | ✅ verified via :3050 |\n| `list_services` | `GET /api/admin/services` | collabmind-api internal | " --context documentation --tags "source:docs,type:documentation"

