# hindsight_sync_retain --bank_id documentation --content "# Readme\n\n# CollabMind MCP Gateway\n\nExposes CollabMind platform capabilities as MCP tools.\nAll tools call the Central API (`collabmind-api` at `:3050`) only — no direct backend access.\n\n## Architecture\n\n```\nMCP Client (Claude, Cursor, etc.)\n  → collabmind-mcp (this package, stdio)\n    → collabmind-api :3050  (auth edge, audit, proxy)\n      → memory-controller :3020\n      → document-service  :3030\n      → model-gateway     :3031\n      → evaluation        :3032\n      → Graphiti          :8001  (not yet running)\n```\n\nOpenMemory `:18080` is an internal backend of memory-controller, not directly accessible via MCP.\n\n## Setup\n\n```bash\ncp .env.example .env\n# Set COLLABMIND_API_URL and COLLABMIND_MCP_API_KEY\nnpm install\nnpm run build\n```\n\n## Run\n\n```bash\nnpm start          # production\nnpm run dev        # development (tsx watch)\n```\n\n## Add to Claude Desktop\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"collabmind\": {\n      \"command\": \"node\",\n      \"args\": [\"/path/to/collabmind-mcp/dist/index.js\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"COLLABMIND_API_URL\": \"http://localhost:3050\",\n        \"COLLABMIND_MCP_API_KEY\": \"<your-api-key>\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Auth\n\nSet exactly one of:\n- `COLLABMIND_MCP_API_KEY` → sent as `X-Api-Key` header\n- `COLLABMIND_SERVICE_TOKEN` → sent as `Authorization: Bearer <token>`\n\nDo not hardcode secrets. Do not commit `.env`.\n\n## Runtime Status\n\n`:3050` (`collabmind-api`) is live. 7/15 tools working. 4 tools have known routing bugs being fixed.\nSee `MCP_TOOLS.md` for full status and `docs/runtime/mcp-runtime-reconciliation.md` for bug details.\n\n## Tools\n\nSee `MCP_TOOLS.md` for full tool reference and runtime status.\n" --context documentation --tags "source:docs,type:documentation"

